rule-16-5-a.test_description: A proposed building has an elevator. The baseline of that building has an elevator with cab ventilation and lights running continuously as expected. Expected result: PASS

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously

rule-16-5-b.test_description: A proposed building has an elevator. The baseline of that building has an elevator with cab ventilation that does not run continuously. Expected result: FAIL

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously

rule-16-5-c.test_description: A proposed building has an elevator. Neither the proposed or baseline of that building has an elevator cab ventilation schedule. Expected result: FAIL

standard.rule_description: When included in the proposed design, the baseline elevator cab ventilation fan and lights shall operate continuously
